snippet.title: Rosanna Pansino - Perfect Together (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Available on iTunes!: http://tinyurl.com/lt3q9ux
Google Play: http://tinyurl.com/lcj4mhn
Amazon Music: http://tinyurl.com/q5r4w2m

Download Sheet Music (free!): http://tinyurl.com/qhuuane

Lyrics (free!): http://tinyurl.com/PerfectTogetherLyrics

I am so excited to share with you my very first music video and original song, "Perfect Together". I have done musical theater as far back as high school and have always wanted to make my own song.

A special thanks to everyone who helped make this video possible, from the dancers, makeup artists, wardrobe, guest stars, crew, and anyone who watches this video. Without all of you this video would not have been possible!

snippet.title: Baking Cakes with The Try Guys!
snippet.description:

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/tryguys
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
RECIPE:
Chiffon Cake:
1 1/2 cups all-purpose flour
1 teaspoon baking powder
1/2 teaspoon baking soda
1/2 teaspoon salt
1 1/2 cups sugar
1/2 cup water
1/2 cup vegetable oil
1 1/2 teaspoons vanilla extract
Seeds of 1/2 vanilla bean
6 large eggs, separated
1/2 cup tart candies, finely crushed

Filling:
Swiss Buttercream Frosting
1/2 cup seedless raspberry jam

Pouring Fondant:
1 1/2 cups white chocolate chips
4 1/2 cups powdered sugar, sifted
1/4 cup light corn syrup
6 tablespoons hot water
1 teaspoon vanilla extract
1/4 teaspoon almond extract

1) Melt chocolate chips.
2) In large bowl, mix powdered sugar, corn syrup, hot water, vanilla, and almond extract until smooth.
3) Fold in the melted chocolate until well combined.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Loved making these #Valentines Heart #Cake with the #TryGuys! We used a delicious Petit Fours recipe from my new cookbook Baking All Year Round. We had a lot of fun cooking, playing, singing and dancing! Love these guys! Subscribe for more videos.

xoxo Ro
